#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>CRM App</b>: Manage your leads effectively, tracking ongoing tattoo "
"projects and consultations to ensure no client request is lost."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application CRM</b> : gérez efficacement vos pistes en suivant les "
"projets de tatouage en cours et les consultations, afin de ne perdre aucune "
"demande client."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Purchase App</b>: Automate the restocking of essential supplies like ink, "
"gloves, and needles to ensure you never run out during a session."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Achats</b> : automatisez le réapprovisionnement de vos "
"fournitures essentielles et assurez-vous de ne jamais manquer d’encre, de "
"gants ou d’aiguilles pendant une séance."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Sign App</b>: Handle critical compliance by managing consent forms and "
"important waivers effortlessly with secure digital signatures."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Signature</b> : gérez facilement les exigences de conformité "
"en administrant les formulaires de consentement et les décharges importantes "
"grâce à des signatures numériques sécurisées."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Social Marketing App</b>: Amplify your reach by sharing your latest "
"creations across social platforms and engaging with your audience "
"centrally.Restock supplies with ease using the <strong>Purchase App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Marketing Social</b> : développez votre visibilité en "
"partageant vos dernières créations sur les réseaux sociaux et en "
"interagissant avec votre audience de manière centralisée. Réapprovisionnez "
"facilement vos stocks grâce à l’<strong>application Achats</strong>."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Website App</b>: Build a stunning online portfolio to showcase your work "
"and attract new clients with a professional digital presence."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Site Web</b> : créez un portfolio en ligne attrayant pour "
"présenter votre travail et attirer de nouveaux clients grâce à une présence "
"numérique professionnelle."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:tattoo_shop.about_us
msgid "<br/> Get tattoos that reflect your dedication to self-expression."
msgstr "<br/> Exprimez pleinement votre identité à travers des tatouages."

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tattoo_shop.mail_template_booking_mail
msgid ""
"<div data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n"
"            Hi <t t-out=\"object.contact_name or ''\"/>,\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Don't hesitate to book an appointment with us if you're "
"interested in booking our services.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Here's the link:\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <a t-att-href=\"'/appointment/' + "
"str(env.ref('tattoo_shop.appointment_type_1').id)\">Book Now</a>\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Have a nice day!\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            <t t-out=\"object.user_id.signature\"/></div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n"
"            Bonjour <t t-out=\"object.contact_name or ''\"/>\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Vous avez envie de profiter de nos services ? Il suffit de "
"réserver un rendez-vous.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Voici le lien :\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <a t-att-href=\"'/appointment/' + str(env.ref"
"('tattoo_shop.appointment_type_1').id)\">Réserver maintenant</a>\n"
