"            Bonne journée !\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            <t t-out=\"object.user_id.signature\"/></div>\n"
"        "

#. module: tattoo_shop
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tattoo_shop.mail_template_after_care
msgid ""
"<div data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n"
"            Hi <t t-out=\"object.contact_name or ''\"/>,\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            We hope you had a nice experience at our Tattoo shop.\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            In attachment, you'll find a tattoo aftercare sheet for some "
"tips and tricks.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Have a nice day,\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            <t t-out=\"object.activity_user_id.signature\"/>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n"
"            Bonjour <t t-out=\"object.contact_name or ''\"/>\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"          Nous espérons que l’expérience dans notre salon de tatouage a été "
"à la hauteur de vos attentes !\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Une fiche de soins après-tatouage est jointe, avec quelques "
"conseils pratiques.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Bonne journée,\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            <t t-out=\"object.activity_user_id.signature\"/>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "

